    requirement: "Per volume, the figure/visual workflow is TWO-STAGE in this order: (1) DETAILED figures authored + pushed to the seeit interactive surface FIRST (full-resolution, full-detail, interactive/zoomable); (2) THEN the SIMPLIFIED, print-legible book visuals derived from them (enlarged type, reduced detail) embedded in the manuscript. Detail lives in seeit; the book carries the simplified version + a pointer to seeit."
